<h5 class="post_author"><a class="author" href="/franshizi2017" data-from-id="-68113099" data-post-id="-68113099_4295" data-post-click-type="post_owner_link">&#9733;Идеи для Бизнеса&#9733;Мотивация&#9733;Online развитие</a> <span class="explain"><span class="wall_fixed_label"> pinned post</span></span></h5>
 <div class="post_date"><a class="post_link" href="/wall-68113099_4295" onclick="return showWiki({w: 'wall-68113099_4295'}, false, event);" ><span class="rel_date">21 May at 6:06 pm</span></a></div>
 <div class="ui_actions_menu_wrap _ui_menu_wrap " onmouseover="uiActionsMenu.show(this);" onmouseout="uiActionsMenu.hide(this);">
 <div class="ui_actions_menu_icons" tabindex="0" aria-label="Actions" role="button" onclick="uiActionsMenu.keyToggle(this, event);"><span class="blind_label">Actions</span></div>
 <div class="ui_actions_menu _ui_menu" ><a class="ui_actions_menu_item" onclick="wall.markAsSpam(this, '-68113099_4295', '1777674d5600794dc9');" tabindex="0" role="link">Report</a></div>
